== 禱文 ==
一篇常見於[[正教會|東正教]]和某些{{tsl|en|Folk Catholicism|民間天主教}}傳統中通用的聖巴拉基勒禱文如下：

{{lang|en|O Powerful Archangel, St. Barachiel, filled with heaven's glory and splendour, you are rightly called God's benediction. We are God's children placed under your protection and care. Hear our supplications (name them). Grant that, through your loving intercession, we may reach our heavenly home one day. Sustain us and protect us from all harm that we may possess for all eternity the peace and happiness that Jesus has prepared for us in heaven. Present God the Father all these petitions, through Jesus Christ, our Lord, together with the Holy Spirit, forever and ever. Amen.}}

